Package: yfR
Title: Downloads and Organizes Financial Data from Yahoo Finance
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Marcelo", "Perlin", email = "marceloperlin@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Makes it easy to download financial data from Yahoo Finance <https://finance.yahoo.com/>, 
 a vast repository of stock price data accross multiple financial exchanges. The package offers a local caching system
 and support for parallel computation.
Date: 2022-03-28
URL: https://github.com/msperlin/yfR
BugReports: https://github.com/msperlin/yfR/issues
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1)
Imports: stringr, curl, XML, tidyr, 
    lubridate, furrr, purrr, future, tibble, zoo, crayon,
    cli, readr, rvest, dplyr, quantmod
License: GPL-2
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.2
Suggests: knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat,
    ggplot2
VignetteBuilder: knitr
